itunes:subtitle: Ross Patterson, Mat Best, Jarred Taylor, and Dan Hollaway are joined by Asking Alexandria frontman Danny Worsnop as they get as drunk as they possibly can on the Drinkin' Bros Cruise in the Gulf Of Mexico, and we managed to get some form of audio from a ...
itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Mat Best, Jarred Taylor, and Dan Hollaway are joined by Asking Alexandria frontman Danny Worsnop as they get as drunk as they possibly can on the Drinkin' Bros Cruise in the Gulf Of Mexico, and we managed to get some form of audio from a Carribean man who recorded the show.  Jarred was the drunkest we've ever seen him.  This was one of the best times of our lives and we can't thank you enough for coming out!
